track_notes: Pleasant excursion starting from the village of Promiod and ascending in the wide homonymous valley. Once at Col Portola you can admire the splendid panorama of the Monte Rosa group.

North way is shorter but steeper. Better do it in summer in half time. 
Today very hard for a lot of snow.
track_title: class EE ,  North track, phone OK ,  statue on  summit

track_notes:
